The following query searches for movies with the characters `off` in
the `title` field.**Atlas UI:**Atlas UICopy and paste the following query into the
**Query Editor**, and then click the **Search**
button in the **Query Editor**.```javascript
[
  {
    $search: {
      autocomplete: {
        path: "title",
        query: "off"
      }
    }
  }
]
```**Shell:**MongoDB ShellThe query includes a:* [$limit](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/limit) stage to limit the output to 10 results.

* [$project](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/project) stage to exclude all fields except `title`.```javascript
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    $search: {
      "autocomplete": {
        "path": "title",
        "query": "off"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    $limit: 10
  },
  {
    $project: {
      "_id": 0,
      "title": 1
    }
  }
])

```**Compass:**CompassThe query includes a:* [$limit](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/limit) stage to limit the output to 10 results.

